"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?10/62/11238/abstract/2\">",
"      Schwartz GJ, Haycock GB, Edelmann CM Jr, Spitzer A. A simple estimate of glomerular filtration rate in children derived from body length and plasma creatinine. Pediatrics 1976; 58:259.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?10/62/11238/abstract/3\">",
"      Counahan R, Chantler C, Ghazali S, et al. Estimation of glomerular filtration rate from plasma creatinine concentration in children. Arch Dis Child 1976; 51:875.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?10/62/11238/abstract/4\">",
